    "excerpt": "A pizmon for Shabbat Zakhor and Purim, found in many Livorno siddurim (seen as the standard form for most Sephardic communities) as far back as the 18th century and possibly earlier. It is signed with the name Avraham, as well as the names Moshe and Aharon, but the author is otherwise unknown. Seder Mishmeret haKodesh (1847) inserts it as an introduction to the Mi Khamokha piyyut of Yehuda haLevi, recited on Shabbat Zakhor. The bouncy, joyous tune used for this piyyut, of Italian origin, is also used for Purim songs in multiple languages, such as Fate Onore al Bel Purim, Con Gran Placer Señores, and Haman Mamzer el Malo.",
    "content": "<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\nA pizmon for Shabbat Zakhor and Purim, found in many Livorno siddurim (seen as the standard form for most Sephardic communities) as far back as the 18th century and possibly earlier. It is signed with the name Avraham, as well as the names Mosheh and Aharon, but the author is otherwise unknown. <em>Seder Mishmeret haKodesh</em> (1847) inserts it as an introduction to the Mi Khamokha piyyut of Yehuda haLevi, recited on Shabbat Zakhor. The bouncy, joyous tune used for this piyyut, of Italian origin, is also used for Purim songs in multiple languages, such as Fate Onore al Bel Purim, Con Gran Placer Señores, and Haman Mamzer el Malo.\n</div>\n<hr />\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">אַ</span>ךְ זֶה הַיּוֹם קִוִּֽיתִי<br />\nלָשִׁיר אֶת־נִקְמַת צָר<br />\nבּוֹ מָצָֽאתִי רָאִֽיתִי<br />\nיֶֽשַׁע מִן־הַמֵּצַר<br />\nאָגִֽילָה<br />\nאַגְדִּֽילָה<br />\nאֶל־צוּר אֵלַי מִבְצָר<br />\nמֵחֶֽרֶב הַיּוֹנָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nYea, this very day I have hoped,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Lamentations 2:16&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nto sing of avenging the foe!<br />\nUpon it I have found,<br />\nI have seen salvation from the straits.<br />\nLet me acclaim,<br />\nlet me greaten<br />\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">the Rock</span> who is my fortress;<br />\nfrom the sword came the dove<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Israel. Taking a crux phrase in Jeremiah 46:16 and 50:16 and reframing it.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">בַּ</span>כֶּֽסֶף אָז קָנָֽנִי<br />\nאִישׁ זֵד צוֹרֵר הָרָע<br />\nצֹאן לַטֶּֽבַח שָׂמָֽנִי<br />\nכִּי צַדִּיק לֹא כָרַע<br />\nאַךְ שֶֽׁקֶר<br />\nכׇּל־חֵֽקֶר<br />\nהֶֽבֶל רֽוּחַ זָרַע<br />\nחַי אֵל אוֹיֵב פִּנָּה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nHe bought me with silver,<br />\nthe arrogant oppressing evil man.<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Haman&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nHe set me as sheep to the slaughter,<br />\nfor the righteous one<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Mordechai&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> had not bowed.<br />\nYea, false<br />\nwas every inquiry,<br />\nsighs sowing wind.<br />\nLiving is <span class=\"divine-referent\">the Deity</span> who cleared off the enemy,<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">רָ</span>שָׁע נָחָשׁ בָּרִֽיחַ<br />\nאָז בְּכֹֽחַ וָאֵל<br />\nפִּתָּה מֶֽלֶךְ הִדִּֽיחַ<br />\nלַשְׁמִיד אֶת־יִשְׂרָאֵל<br />\nתַּם רֶֽשַׁע<br />\nבָּא יֶֽשַׁע<br />\nמִלֹּא הִשְׁבִּית גּוֹאֵל<br />\nעַל־יַד אִישׁ חַרְבוֹנָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nThe wicked elusive snake<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Isaiah 27:1, Job 26:13&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nthen, in power and force,<br />\nenticed and seduced the king<br />\nto destroy Israel.<br />\nThe wicked one ended,<br />\nsalvation came,<br />\nfrom <span class=\"divine-referent\">the Redeemer</span> not witheld,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Find Ruth 4:14&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nby the hand of the man Ḥarvona,<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">הָ</span>מָן וּבְנֵי הַבַּֽיִת<br />\nכֻּלָּם עַל־עֵץ נִתְלוּ<br />\nהוֹדִי עָלַי כַּזַּֽיִת<br />\nאַךְ שָׂרִים נִבְהָֽלוּ<br />\nזַמֵּֽרוּ<br />\nדַּבֵּֽרוּ<br />\nחַסְדֵּי־אֵל לֹא יִכְלוּ<br />\nעַד־שֵׂיבָה עַד־זִקְנָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nHaman and his household <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nall were hanged on wood.<br />\nMy splendor is upon me like an olive-tree;<br />\nyea, princes are astonished!<br />\nSing,<br />\nspeak<br />\nof <span class=\"divine-referent\">the Deity</span>’s mercies unending<br />\nuntil hoary old age,<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">מַ</span>הֵר שִׂמְחוּ גַּם גִּֽילוּ<br />\nעִמִּי אַחַי רֵעָי<br />\nיַֽיִן שֵׁכָר הוֹבִֽילוּ<br />\nעַתָּה אֶל־תּוֹךְ מֵעָי<br />\nהָכִֽינוּ<br />\nהַרְנִֽינוּ<br />\nשִֽׂישׂוּ אֶל־שַׁעֲשׁוּעָי<br />\nכׇּל־פֶּֽלֶךְ וּמְדִינָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nHurry, be happy and acclaim with me, <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nmy siblings and friends!<br />\nGuide wine and cider<br />\nnow into my gut!<br />\nPrepare,<br />\ncheer out,<br />\nrejoice to my delights,<br />\nevery province and territory<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">חִזְק</span>וּ בָאֵל לִבְטֹֽחַ<br />\nכִּי יִוָּסֵד הֵיכָל<br />\nקָמִים גִּבּוֹרֵי כֹֽחַ<br />\nמָחָר חֶֽרֶב תֹּאכַל<br />\nנָקֽוּמָה<br />\nנָרֽוּמָה<br />\nמַלְכֵּֽנוּ כֹּל יוּכַל<br />\nחִישׁ תָּדוּץ אַלְמָנָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nBe strong in <span class=\"divine-referent\">the Deity</span> to trust <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\nthat the Palace will be established.<br />\nStrongmen rising against us tomorrow,<br />\nthe sword will consume.<br />\nLet’s rise up,<br />\nlet’s exalt<br />\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">our omnipotent Sovereign</span>!<br />\nSpeedily cheer up the widow<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">מִֽ</span>מְּכוֹן־שִׁׄבְתּ֥וֹ הִׄשְׁגִּ֑יחַ<br />\nאֲׄזַי הָׄאֵל רַׄחְמָן<br />\nנָׄתַץ כָּרַת הִרְתִּֽיחַ<br />\nזֵֽכֶר זֶֽרַע הָמָן<br />\nהוֹבִֽישׁוּ<br />\nהוֹבִֽישׁוּ<br />\nגַּם הֵם כְּשֹׁ֧ד שַֽׁלְמַ֛ן<br />\nוּפָרְחָה שׁוֹשַׁנָּה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\nThen, from <span class=\"divine-referent\">Their</span> dwelling-place <span class=\"acrostic\">&nbsp;</span><br />\ngazed down<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Psalms 33:14&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"divine-referent\">the compassionate Deity</span>.<br />\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">They</span> smashed, cut down, boiled up<br />\nthe memory of Haman’s seed.<br />\nThey were ashamed,<br />\nashamed,<br />\nas peaceniks plundered!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Hosea 10:14&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnd the rose<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Israel, from the allegorical reading of Song of Songs.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> flowered<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\nמוֹצִ֣יא אֲ֭סִירִים פּוֹדֶה<br />\nמֶ֭לֶךְ עוֹלָ֣ם וָעֶ֑ד<br />\nכׇּל־צַר צוֹרֵר צוֹדֶה<br />\nהַכְרֵת כִּי־בָ֥א מוֹעֵֽד׃<br />\nיַעְתִּֽירוּ<br />\nיַקְטִֽירוּ<br />\nפֶּֽתַח אֹֽהֶל מוֹעֵד<br />\nמׇר־דְּרוֹר עִם־לְבֹנָה<br />\nבְּשִׂמְחָה וּבִרְנָנָה׃\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">Freer of prisoners</span>,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Psalms 68:7&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> <span class=\"divine-referent\">Ransomer</span>,<br />\n<span class=\"divine-referent\">Sovereign</span> eternal and aye;<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Psalms 10:16&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nevery stressing foe lies in wait;<br />\ncut them down, for the time has come!<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[12]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Psalms 102:14&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nThey will pray,<br />\nburn incense<br />\nat the entrance to the Tent of Meeting;<br />\npure myrrh<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[13]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Also a reference to Mordechai, according to Megillah 10b.&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script> with frankincense<br />\nin joy and in cheer!\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<p><span style=\"float: right;\"><div id=\"attachment_66246\" style=\"width: 260px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--115v.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-66246\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--115v-250x250.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-66246\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-66246\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Akh Zeh HaYom Kiviti (Mishmeret haqodesh livorno 1847), p. 115v</p></div></span> <span style=\"float: left;\"><div id=\"attachment_66247\" style=\"width: 260px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--116r.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-66247\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--116r-250x250.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-66247\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-66247\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Akh Zeh HaYom Kiviti (Mishmeret haqodesh livorno 1847), p. 116r</p></div></span> <span style=\"float: left;\"><div id=\"attachment_66248\" style=\"width: 260px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--116v.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-66248\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/akh-zeh-hayom-kiviti-mishmeret-haqodesh-livorno-1847-p--116v-250x250.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-66248\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-66248\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Akh Zeh HaYom Kiviti (Mishmeret haqodesh livorno 1847), p. 116v</p></div></span><span class=\"\" style=\"display:block;clear:both;height: 0px;margin-top: ;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;\"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Lamentations 2:16</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >2</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Israel. Taking a crux phrase in Jeremiah 46:16 and 50:16 and reframing it.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >3</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Haman</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >4</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Mordechai</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >5</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Isaiah 27:1, Job 26:13</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >6</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Find Ruth 4:14</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >7</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Psalms 33:14</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >8</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Hosea 10:14</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >9</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Israel, from the allegorical reading of Song of Songs.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >10</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Psalms 68:7</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >11</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Psalms 10:16</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >12</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Psalms 102:14</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >13</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Also a reference to Mordechai, according to Megillah 10b.</td></tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody> </table> </div></div><script type=\"text/javascript\"> function footnote_expand_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').show(); jQuery('#footnote_reference_container_collapse_button__1').text('−'); } function footnote_collapse_reference_container__1() { jQuery('#footnote_references_container__1').hide(); jQuery('#fo